{"vv35:0.1":"Vimanavatthu ","vv35:0.2":"Itthivimana ","vv35:0.3":"Paricchattakavagga ","vv35:0.4":"7. Pesavativimanavatthu ","vv35:1.1":"“Phalikarajatahemajalachannam, ","vv35:1.2":"Vividhacitratalamaddasam surammam; ","vv35:1.3":"Byamham sunimmitam toranupapannam, ","vv35:1.4":"Rucakupakinnamidam subham vimanam. ","vv35:2.1":"Bhati ca dasa disa nabheva suriyo, ","vv35:2.2":"Sarade tamonudo sahassaramsi; ","vv35:2.3":"Tatha tapati midam tava vimanam, ","vv35:2.4":"Jalamiva dhumasikho nise nabhagge. ","vv35:3.1":"Musativa nayanam sateratava, ","vv35:3.2":"Akase thapitamidam manunnam; ","vv35:3.3":"Vinamurajasammatalaghuttham, ","vv35:3.4":"Iddham indapuram yatha tavedam. ","vv35:4.1":"Padumakumuduppalakuvalayam, ","vv35:4.2":"Yodhika bandhukanojaka ca santi; ","vv35:4.3":"Salakusumitapupphita asoka, ","vv35:4.4":"Vividhadumaggasugandhasevitamidam. ","vv35:5.1":"Salalalabujabhujaka samyutta, ","vv35:5.2":"Kusakasuphullitalatavalambinihi; ","vv35:5.3":"Manijalasadisa yasassini, ","vv35:5.4":"Ramma pokkharani upatthita te. ","vv35:6.1":"Udakaruha ca yetthi pupphajata, ","vv35:6.2":"Thalaja ye ca santi rukkhajata; ","vv35:6.3":"Manusakamanussaka ca dibba, ","vv35:6.4":"Sabbe tuyham nivesanamhi jata. ","vv35:7.1":"Kissa samyamadamassayam vipako, ","vv35:7.2":"Kenasi kammaphalenidhupapanna; ","vv35:7.3":"Yatha ca te adhigatamidam vimanam, ","vv35:7.4":"Tadanupadam avacasilarapamhe”ti. ","vv35:8.1":"“Yatha ca me adhigatamidam vimanam, ","vv35:8.2":"Koncamayuracakorasanghacaritam; ","vv35:8.3":"Dibyapilavahamsarajacinnam, ","vv35:8.4":"Dijakarandavakokilabhinaditam. ","vv35:9.1":"Nanasantanakapuppharukkhavividha, ","vv35:9.2":"Patalijambuasokarukkhavantam; ","vv35:9.3":"Yatha ca me adhigatamidam vimanam, ","vv35:9.4":"Tam te pavedayami sunohi bhante. ","vv35:10.1":"Magadhavarapuratthimena, ","vv35:10.2":"Nalakagamo nama atthi bhante; ","vv35:10.3":"Tattha ahosim pure sunisa, ","vv35:10.4":"Pesavatiti tattha janimsu mamam. ","vv35:11.1":"Sahamapacitatthadhammakusalam, ","vv35:11.2":"Devamanussapujitam mahantam; ","vv35:11.3":"Upatissam nibbutamappameyyam, ","vv35:11.4":"Muditamana kusumehi abbhukirim. ","vv35:12.1":"Paramagatigatanca pujayitva, ","vv35:12.2":"Antimadehadharam isim ularam; ","vv35:12.3":"Pahaya manusakam samussayam, ","vv35:12.4":"Tidasagata idha mavasami thanan”ti. ","vv35:13.1":"Pesavativimanam sattamam. "}